name: Calypso - Extended Reality Artwork -
description: "The wind deeply scarred the ocean, We were like driftwood chips on a puddle, A raging storm began to devour the sails  Like a dream, Calypso emerged from the waters.  In her rise, the hope of returning to earth.  This land became our treasure today.  The cursed game eventually came to an end, We so quickly forget the value of things, Blind, as if everything was eternal.  We are coming home."  Cyril Rolando – Aquasixio x Cédric Rolando – Neoyume  Cyril’s original artwork “Calypso” , 3D sculpted and painted by Cédric.  3D textured model, .glb file format.  You can display this sculpture in Augmented Reality thanks to a compatible device.  More informations https://neoyume.com/era/
